#: ..\..\source\GettingStartedGuide\mayatutorials.rst:9
msgid ""
"In this tutorial you will learn how to drive the position of a locator using"
" Canvas. This is the first step towards using Canvas for rigging. Since "
"|FABRIC_PRODUCT_NAME| provides a portable solution for any custom node "
"within Maya, you'll be able to build flexible kinematic solutions which are "
"portable between applications."
msgstr ""

